## Added
* HTR-F4 Fusion Plasma Thruster
  * Utilises plasma generated within a Plasma Heater as a potent thruster fuel
  * Set the plasma type in the heater before placing the thruster to automatically set the plasma type
* Double barrel shotgun (from [X5193](https://github.com/HbmMods/Hbm-s-Nuclear-Tech-GIT/releases/tag/1.0.27_X5193))
  * Special weapon, spawns as part of certain loot pools
  * Uses the new 10 gauge caliber
  * Will reload after each shot, however it is not belt-fed, if ammo is depleted, the next reload must be triggered manually

## Changed
* HTR-3 renamed to LPW-3N, which can now also use all new nuclear fuels which all function as PWR coolants. a Fluid ID can be used to change fuel types
* Removed the old casing items
* Reduced the flicker on the autoshotgun's holo sights

## Fixed
* All fixes from upstream NTM - [X5193](https://github.com/HbmMods/Hbm-s-Nuclear-Tech-GIT/releases/tag/1.0.27_X5193)
